carousel_media.accessibility_caption:
First page of the Xbox Game Pass Game Fair flyer featuring multiple different games to choose from, with descriptions of each game. Text reads: "XBOX GAME PASS GAME FAIR | Choose Games You'll Love to Play

1. Tell Me Why - In this intimate mystery, reunited twins Tyler and Alyson Ronan use their supernatural bond to unravel the memories of their loving but troubled childhood. Set in beautiful small-town Alaska, Tell Me Why features true-to-life characters, mature themes and gripping choices.

2. Broken Age - A timeless coming-of-age story of two teenagers in strangely similar situations, but radically different worlds. Also features barfing trees and talking spoons.

3. Lies of P [NEW] - Lies of P is a thrilling soulslike that takes the story of Pinocchio, turns it on its head, and sets it against the darkly elegant backdrop of the Belle Epoque era. You are a puppet created by Geppetto who's caught in a web of lies."

Second page of the Xbox Game Pass Game Fair flyer featuring multiple different games to choose from with descriptions of each game, as well as a poster. Text reads:

POSTER: Yoked Girth - You'll feel strong and powerful when you hang this in your room. Full color poster. 24" x 18"

4. Pentiment [STAFF PICK] - Walk in the footsteps of Andreas Maler, a master artist who finds himself in the middle of murders, scandals, and intrigue in the Bavarian Alps.

5. A Plague Tale: Requiem - Far across the sea, an island calls... Embark on a heartrending journey into a brutal, breathtaking world twisted by supernatural forces.

6. As Dusk Falls - As Dusk Falls is an original interactive drama from INTERIOR/NIGHT that explores the entangled lives of two families across thirty years. Starting in 1998 with a robbery-gone-wrong in small town Arizona, the choices you make have a powerful impact on the characters' lives in this uncompromising story of betrayal, sacrifice and resilience."

Third and final page of the Xbox Game Pass Game Fair flyer featuring an order form on the left with a dotted 'cut here' line down the middle and multiple different games to choose from on the right. The order form lists each title from 1 - 8 with a 'Qty.' box next to each one to let you order the games you want. Text reads: XBOX GAME PASS GAME FAIR Game Club Order Form: Please select how many you want to play | TOTAL GAMES TO PLAY

7. Starfield - The year is 2330. Humanity has ventured beyond our solar system, settling new planets, and living as a spacefaring people.

8. Phoenix Wright: Ace Attorney Trilogy - Join Phoenix Wright in his fight against injustice as he takes on a series of courtroom catastrophes! With three Ace Attorney games in one package, you'll encounter a myriad of quirky characters, intriguing investigations, and mind-bending mysteries."

caption.text: POV it's a crisp fall day at school and your parent said you can pick 3 games from the game fair
